  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2 class="cv-section-title">About the piece</h2>
    <p class="cv-body">
      Spiegel im Spiegel ("Mirror in the Mirror") is a 1978 composition by Arvo Pärt
      for piano and violin. Its structure is deceptively simple: a single melodic line
      expands outward and contracts inward in a mirror pattern. I wrote a Ruby program
      that models this structure algorithmically and plays it through Sonic Pi, a
      live-coding music environment built on Ruby.
    </p>
    <p class="cv-body mt-3">
      To run this yourself, paste the code into
      <a href="https://sonic-pi.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-link">Sonic Pi</a>
      (free download) and press Run.
    </p>
  </section>

